[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0399","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0399.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0213","title":"Sun Solaris rpcbind libnsl 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 的 rpcbind 服务中的 libnsl 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 rpcbind 服务发送特制的 RPC 请求，导致 libnsl 库处理异常，进而使 rpcbind 服务崩溃或进入不可响应状态。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.4、2.5、2.5.1 及 2.6 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害严重。厂商 Sun 已发布安全补丁，建议用户及时升级修复。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0213"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.537","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 针对此漏洞发布的对应 Solaris 版本补丁集（如 Patch ID 106235 等），将系统升级至最新支持版本。如无法修补，可在 /etc/init.d/rpc 中禁用 rpcbind 服务，或在防火墙上限制外部对 UDP/TCP 端口 111 的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9749"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0399.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0028","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0028.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0006","title":"Qualcomm qpopper POP3 服务器缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Qualcomm qpopper 2.4 及之前版本的 POP3 服务器存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送超长的 PASS 命令参数即可触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行并以 root 权限完全控制系统。该漏洞无需特殊权限即可远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0006"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-07-14","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 qpopper 至 2.5 及以上版本，该版本修复了 PASS 命令处理中的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。若无法升级，在 inetd/xinetd 配置中对 qpopper 服务启用 TCP wrapper 访问控制（hosts.allow/hosts.deny），限制允许连接 POP 服务的源 IP 范围。对于已停止维护的旧系统，建议迁移至现代 POP3/IMAP 服务器（如 Dovecot），并禁用不再安全的 POP3 协议。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/133"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0028.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1272","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1272.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1434","title":"Slackware Linux 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Slackware Linux 3.2 至 3.5 版本的 login 程序在 /etc/group 文件缺失时未正确检查错误，导致无法正确降权，导致任意本地用户登录系统即可获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Slackware Linux 3.2 至 3.5 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危）。攻击者只需拥有本地登录权限，在 /etc/group 文件缺失的条件下登录系统即可获得 root 权限，属于本地权限提升漏洞。官方已在后续版本中修复该漏洞，建议升级至 Slackware Linux 3.6 或更高版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1434"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:25.980","remediation":"升级到 Slackware Linux 5.0 或更高版本，其中包含对 /etc/group 文件存在性检查的修复，或立即手动创建 /etc/group 文件并确保权限为 644，防止登录过程因文件缺失导致 root 权限错误分配。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525951&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/155","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19122","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1434.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1434","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1434.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1434.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gf33-x5h5-m638/GHSA-gf33-x5h5-m638.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/155/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1434.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000331.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ed4391f8-390c-46cc-8693-11a66005d78f.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1272.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1272.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1272.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1439","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1439.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1270","title":"KDE Kmail PGP密钥口令泄露漏洞","description":"KDE 1.0 中的 Kmail 邮件客户端存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。Kmail 在调用外部程序处理 PGP 加密邮件时，将 PGP 私钥密码以命令行参数形式传递给子进程，导致本地攻击者可通过 ps 等进程列表工具查看其他用户的命令行参数，从而获取 PGP 密码并解密或伪造其加密通信。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.0 版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1270"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-07-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.823","remediation":"升级到 KDE 1.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复将 PGP 口令作为命令行参数传递的问题，改用标准输入传递口令防止被其他进程窃取。如无法升级，可使用 gpg-agent 缓存口令避免每次输入。限制不可信用户登录系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.kde.org/?l=kde-devel&m=90221974029738&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1639","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1270.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1270","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1270.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1270.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5m8h-jjf9-c2p5/GHSA-5m8h-jjf9-c2p5.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87816/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1270.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-214.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_infor.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1439.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0235","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0235.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0102","title":"SLmail 3.x 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"SLmail 3.x 邮件服务器在处理邮件头 FROM 字段时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送含有超长 FROM 行的特制邮件触发该漏洞，导致内存越界写入，从而实现以邮件服务进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 SLmail 3.x 全系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0102"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:35.467","remediation":"立即升级 SLMail 至 3.2.0.3 以上版本，该版本修复了 FROM 行缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，应在边界防火墙上限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 SMTP 端口（25/tcp），并考虑迁移至长期维护的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix 或 Exchange）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0102"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0235.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1273","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1273.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1436","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9147,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10828}}","description":"Ray Chan WWW Authorization Gateway 0.1 版本的 CGI 认证网关程序在处理用户请求时，未对传入的 \"user\" 参数进行充分的输入过滤与转义。远程攻击者可在该参数中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符、反引号等），从而绕过认证逻辑并在目标服务器上以 CGI 进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响运行 0.1 版本 WWW Authorization Gateway 的 Web 服务器，攻击者仅需能访问该 CGI 接口并通过 HTTP 请求提交特制参数即可发起攻击，无需身份认证，可导致服务器被远程控制、数据泄露或服务中断，危害程度较高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1436"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:26.230","remediation":"立即停止部署并移除存在漏洞的 WWW Authorization Gateway 0.1 CGI 程序（删除对应 .cgi 文件），改用 Apache mod_auth 或 Nginx auth_basic 等成熟认证模块替代；若必须短期保留，应在 CGI 脚本中对 user 参数做严格的字母数字白名单过滤并 stripping 所有 shell 元字符（如 ; & | $ ` 等），同时在 Web 服务器层用 mod_security 规则拦截含特殊字符的请求作为缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525905&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/152","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19121","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1436.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1436","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1436.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1436.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jgj2-qg73-9762/GHSA-jgj2-qg73-9762.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/152/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1436.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000328.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--480bf667-9c0c-4ec4-ba29-fdf8b485d1e7.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1273.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1273.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1273.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1274","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1274.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1437","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9167,\"outputTokens\":29,\"totalTokens\":10860}}","description":"ePerl 2.2.12 版本在处理 ISINDEX 查询时存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 bar.phtml 传递目标文件的完整路径名作为参数，读取服务器上的任意文件，甚至可能执行特定命令。该漏洞影响 ePerl 2.2.12 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5 属高危级别。攻击者无需身份验证即可远程利用，仅需构造包含目标文件绝对路径的请求参数即可实现任意文件读取，严重时可能导致敏感信息泄露或命令执行。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1437"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:26.363","remediation":"建议立即停止使用 ePerl 2.2.12 并迁移至现代 Web 框架（如 PHP、Python、Node.js 等）。若必须继续使用，请在 Web 服务器配置中禁用 ISINDEX 功能，并在 Web 服务器层面限制 bar.phtml 对文件系统的访问权限（如配置 open_basedir、禁用危险函数）。建议部署 WAF 规则拦截包含路径遍历特征的 ISINDEX 查询参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525890&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525927&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/151","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19120","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1437.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1437","https://github.com/CPAN-Security/cpan-advisory-database/blob/bc9ed2336eeed09f48acb0a64fd37970dc5a31d6/triage/CVE-1999-1437.yml","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1437.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1437.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-74xc-6hpg-hp8m/GHSA-74xc-6hpg-hp8m.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1437.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000327.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e155fb1f-b408-4597-af9c-85c151c1d15c.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1274.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1274.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1274.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1392","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1392.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1202","title":"StarTech POP3 Proxy Server与Telnet Server认证长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"StarTech POP3 Proxy Server 和 Telnet Server 存在身份验证拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器的身份验证模块发送超长的 USER 命令，触发缓冲区异常导致服务崩溃。该漏洞影响 StarTech POP3 Proxy Server 及 Telnet Server 相关版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击门槛低。厂商至今未发布官方补丁，建议限制受影响服务的访问来源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1202"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.200","remediation":"建议立即停止使用 StarTech POP3 Proxy Server 和 Telnet Server，改用主流维护中的替代方案（如 Dovecot、Postfix 等现代邮件代理）。如无法替换，应在网络边界防火墙配置规则，限制对 POP3 (110/TCP) 和 Telnet (23/TCP) 端口的来源 IP 白名单访问，防止任意来源的恶意连接。同时，在服务端程序层面建议实现输入长度检查，对 USER 命令参数做长度上限（如 ≤64 字节）截断校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221104525873&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2088","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1202.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1202","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1202.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1202.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3hqc-gjr5-73rx/GHSA-3hqc-gjr5-73rx.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88605/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1202.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--31f64f7c-a00e-4f9b-a656-8fe2f130faa9.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1392.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1266","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1266.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1409","title":"NetBSD 和 SGI IRIX at 命令本地文件读取漏洞","description":"NetBSD 1.3.2 和 SGI IRIX 6.2 及更早版本的 at 计划任务工具存在安全漏洞。该工具在处理 -f 参数时，通过错误消息机制将包含用户提交文件的路径名及文件内容的异常信息以电子邮件形式发送给用户。攻击者可利用此漏洞提交任意文件，诱使系统生成包含敏感内容的文件路径和文件片段的错误消息，最终获取文件的实际内容。此漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.3.2 及更早版本以及 SGI IRIX 6.2 及更早版本。严重危害权限提升和信息泄漏，攻击者仅需在本地环境下即可实施攻击，利用方式直接通过向 at 命令提交目标文件并等待电子邮件回复来获取目标文件内容。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1409"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:22.727","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 到 1.3.3 及以上版本，升级 SGI IRIX 到 6.5.2 及以上版本以修复 at 程序缺陷。临时缓解措施：限制普通用户对 at 命令的使用权限，通过 /etc/at.allow 仅允许授权用户，或移除 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/at）并改用 atd 的访问控制，避免本地用户利用 -f 参数读取任意文件内容。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90233906612929&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7577.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/331","http://www.shmoo.com/mail/bugtraq/jul98/msg00064.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19261","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1409.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1409","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1409.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1409.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-2j9c-282f-c92w/GHSA-2j9c-282f-c92w.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000325.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6abac13e-a9d7-4854-9f11-c053191c8783.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1409.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--6abac13e-a9d7-4854-9f11-c053191c8783.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1266.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1266.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1266.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0745","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0745.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0494","title":"Deerfield WinGate POP3 代理缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"WinGate 代理服务器的 POP3 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 POP3 请求触发该漏洞，导致代理服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 WinGate 多个版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级中等。厂商已发布修复版本，建议用户升级至最新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0494"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.030","remediation":"升级 WinGate 至 2.1d 或更高版本，该版本修复了 POP3 代理中的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可在 WinGate 服务配置中禁用 POP3 代理服务，或通过防火墙限制对 POP3 代理端口（默认 110）的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0494"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0745.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0524","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0524.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0313","title":"SGI IRIX disk_bandwidth 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 S2MP（用于 Origin/Onyx2 服务器）的 disk_bandwidth 工具存在路径遍历漏洞，本地攻击者可通过使用相对路径名欺骗该工具加载恶意动态链接库，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限，利用难度较低，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0313"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.877","remediation":"建议安装 SGI 安全公告 19980701-01-P 提供的修补程序，或升级至 IRIX 6.5 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可移除 disk_bandwidth 程序的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/sbin/disk_bandwidth。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/936","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/213/exploit","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/214","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1441"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0524.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0526","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0526.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0314","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 ioconfig 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 S2MP 系统的 ioconfig 工具在处理相对路径名时未进行充分的安全检查，本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的相对路径利用该漏洞，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.4 操作系统的 Origin/Onyx2 平台，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限才能触发，CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0314"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-07-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"SGI 已于 IRIX 6.5 及后续版本修复此漏洞，建议升级至 IRIX 6.5 或更高版本。如无法升级，可临时移除 ioconfig 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /sbin/ioconfig，或确保 PATH 环境变量中不包含当前目录以避免相对路径劫持。对于仍在运行 SGI IRIX 的生产环境，建议迁移至受支持的替代平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6788","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/213","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/213/exploit","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1199"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0526.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1363","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1150","title":"Livingston Portmaster路由器 TCP初始序列号可预测漏洞","description":"Livingston Portmaster 路由器上运行的 ComOS 操作系统在建立 TCP 连接时使用固定的初始序列号（ISN），导致攻击者无需通过正常的 TCP 三次握手即可预测并伪造序列号。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞构造伪造的 TCP 数据包实施会话劫持或 IP 欺骗攻击，绕过认证机制获取未授权访问。该漏洞影响运行 ComOS 的 Livingston Portmaster 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已不再维护该产品，建议升级至替代方案。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1150"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:49.663","remediation":"升级 ComOS 固件至启用了随机 TCP 初始序列号（ISN）生成的版本（Livingston 已发布相关安全更新）。若无法升级，在网络边界启用 IPsec 加密或 TCP MD5 签名选项（RFC 2385）防止会话劫持与欺骗，同时在路由器 ACL 中限制仅允许可信 IP 访问 Telnet/SSH 管理端口（23/TCP）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9723","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1882","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1150.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1150","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1150.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1150.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vxxg-9388-x757/GHSA-vxxg-9388-x757.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88515/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1150.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--2e3c944c-9364-4251-9a74-0cb99868e123.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1363.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1275","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1275.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1441","title":"Linux Kernel SIGIO 信号本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.34 及早期版本存在权限校验缺陷，未能正确限制普通用户向任意进程发送 SIGIO 信号。本地攻击者无需特殊权限即可向未捕获该信号的进程发送 SIGIO，导致目标进程异常终止或功能失效，从而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0 和 2.1 系列版本，攻击条件要求攻击者拥有目标系统的本地访问权限，利用方式简单直接，仅需通过系统调用发送信号即可完成攻击，无需复杂构造或 elevated 权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1441"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:26.860","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.35 或 2.2.x 及以上版本以修复 SIGIO 信号校验缺陷。若无法立即升级，可通过配置内核限制普通用户向非自身进程发送信号的权限，并在系统层面以非 root 用户运行受影响服务，降低本地拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221103126047&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/111","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19085","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1441.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1441","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1441.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1441.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-464h-jp73-4qp4/GHSA-464h-jp73-4qp4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1441.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/111/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000321.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/9d62a17e1fed77f73d80a5cfda0f78f06970e41d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1275.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1153","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1153.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0797","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9128,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10809}}","description":"SunOS 系统的 NIS（网络信息服务）finger 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。该服务的 finger 守护进程在处理客户端 finger 请求时，每收到一个请求便会向 NIS 服务发起查询。攻击者在未经过身份认证的情况下，可向目标主机连续发送大量 finger 请求，迫使系统产生海量 NIS 查询，从而大量消耗 CPU 与网络资源，最终导致目标系统服务不可用。该漏洞影响运行 SunOS 且启用 NIS 与 finger 服务的系统，本地网络可达的远程攻击者可利用此缺陷实施拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0797"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.677","remediation":"升级到 Sun Solaris 2.6 或更高版本并应用 Sun 安全补丁 105785-01 (SPARC) 或 105786-01 (x86)；或在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 finger 服务并重启 inetd 禁用 finger 服务；或使用 TCP Wrappers (/etc/hosts.allow/deny) 限制 finger 服务仅允许受信任 IP 访问；或在防火墙层面封锁 TCP 79 端口阻断 finger 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-070.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0797.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0797","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0797.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0797.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pj4v-m2mp-56cp/GHSA-pj4v-m2mp-56cp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0797.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88388/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1153.toml"}]